main event: A report was made regarding unidentified flying objects, but no objects were observed. A photograph was submitted for analysis.
interesting points: The original negative of the submitted photo was unavailable., The correspondence indicates confusion over whether the photo was a positive print or an actual sighting., No object was observed during the sighting., No conclusion was reached regarding the sightings., The report references Project Blue Book, a U.S. Air Force program for investigating UFOs.
